not the athleteyou think he is.

03:43.323 --> 03:46.884
- Areyou saying our son is a loser?
- No, of course not. I'm just-

03:46.993 --> 03:49.188
Damn right. Because ifyou're an athlete,
you're a winner.

03:49.295 --> 03:52.059
