paella this weekend.

07:22.308 --> 07:24.776
Great. Now it seems like an obligation
instead ofa treat.

07:24.877 --> 07:27.505
- [ Grinding ]
- Stan, stop grinding yourteeth.

07:27.613 --> 07:30.480
It's notyourfault
that nut-job is still out there.

07:30.583 --> 07:34.383
Forget national security!
We have a real crisis! Our son is a geek!

07:34.487 --> 07:36.887
