14:53.225 --> 14:55.318
Shut up, fatty fat, fat pants!

14:55.427 --> 14:57.918
Wow. Seriously,
I have no idea what that's about.

14:58.030 --> 15:00.521
Only the holder of
the amulet may talk.

15:00.633 --> 15:04.262
